    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2280200/extras/8dee740f6310bcc190cb97a2fbed164e.avif?t=1695294626\" width=600 height=84 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2280200/extras/88cece29b919430a5b0e292e3cb3be9c.poster.avif?t=1695294626\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2280200/extras/88cece29b919430a5b0e292e3cb3be9c.webm?t=1695294626\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2280200/extras/88cece29b919430a5b0e292e3cb3be9c.mp4?t=1695294626\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Search, dream, and sneak to retrieve all of Lucy’s toys with the help of her imaginary friend. <br>Dream Bright offers a refreshing variety by going through 3 cycles each phase.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Explore the large house in search of Lucy's toys<br></li><li> Dream to reach your toy through some enjoyable platforming sections<br></li><li> Sneak through the night and retrieve your toys by avoiding the monsters lurking around the corner</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2280200/extras/2fdbe77a0d19ba835e75dd93f518d5e0.avif?t=1695294626\" width=600 height=84 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2280200/extras/da1b95008a3aa18de7adb64920f40645.poster.avif?t=1695294626\" width=672 height=378 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2280200/extras/da1b95008a3aa18de7adb64920f40645.webm?t=1695294626\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2280200/extras/da1b95008a3aa18de7adb64920f40645.mp4?t=1695294626\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Moving into a new house can feel like a maze.<br>Help Lucy solve puzzles that block her path. <br>Vault, drag, and crouch through her house to discover her toys.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2280200/extras/f825f6c74da93f404a10b685575ab286.avif?t=1695294626\" width=600 height=84 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2280200/extras/2202896f71dcf8e46bb7adc315042bf7.poster.avif?t=1695294626\" width=768 height=432 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2280200/extras/2202896f71dcf8e46bb7adc315042bf7.webm?t=1695294626\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2280200/extras/2202896f71dcf8e46bb7adc315042bf7.mp4?t=1695294626\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Dreaming makes you feel floaty and powerful!<br>Traverse Lucy's dreams together with her companion. <br>Dash and jump through her magical world to approach her toys.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2280200/extras/916cb18d1371b30220b3607328d857ed.avif?t=1695294626\" width=600 height=84 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2280200/extras/e752fd7c9ad8830c79ec32e6afb414a3.poster.avif?t=1695294626\" width=672 height=378 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2280200/extras/e752fd7c9ad8830c79ec32e6afb414a3.webm?t=1695294626\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2280200/extras/e752fd7c9ad8830c79ec32e6afb414a3.mp4?t=1695294626\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>When night falls, the monsters awake. <br>Inanimate objects gain life but will try to take yours. <br>Retrieve Lucy's toys as demons patrol through the house.<br><br><br>This game is made by 6 students from Howest - Digital Arts &amp; Entertainment in the 3rd year of their bachelor.",
